ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR CRYPTOGRAPHIC SOFTWARE

This software contains cryptographic functionality. The use, distribution, and
modification of this software may be subject to applicable laws and regulations
in your jurisdiction regarding cryptographic software.

DISCLAIMER: This software is provided for educational and research purposes.
Users are responsible for ensuring compliance with all applicable laws and
regulations in their jurisdiction. The authors and contributors make no
representations regarding the legal use of this software.

EXPORT CONTROL NOTICE: This distribution includes cryptographic software.
Some countries may restrict the import, possession, use, and/or re-export
of encryption software. Check the laws of your country before using this
software.

SECURITY NOTICE: While this software implements multiple layers of security,
no cryptographic system is absolutely secure. Users should:
1. Keep software updated
2. Use strong, unique passwords
3. Follow security best practices
4. Conduct independent security assessments
5. Report security issues responsibly

For security issues, please contact: security@lackadaisical.dev

