ACKNOWLEDGMENTS

This software incorporates concepts and techniques from various sources:
- BLAKE3 cryptographic hash function
- CRYSTALS-Kyber post-quantum cryptography
- AES-GCM authenticated encryption
- ChaCha20-Poly1305 stream cipher
- RFC standards for HOTP/TOTP
- Various academic research in cryptography

Special thanks to the cryptographic research community for their contributions
to the field of information security.
